<p>
	<strong>Note:  Montana cans are known for spraying erratically with default middles. Purchase these and it will solve everything. I have used these for both Montana Gold and Montana black paints (Thanks to </strong><a data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://thebhg.net/forum/index.php?/profile/13954-tmart77/&amp;do=hovercard&amp;referrer=https%253A%252F%252Fthebhg.net%252Fforum%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F7368-draft-boba-fett-daimyo-bobf-s1-crl%252Fpage%252F6%252F" href="https://thebhg.net/forum/index.php?/profile/13954-tmart77/" rel="" style="background-color:transparent;color:inherit;font-size:16px;" title="Go to Tmart77's profile">Tmart77[501st]</a> for this tip!)
</p>

<p>
	 
</p>

<h1 style="font-size:1.4rem;padding:0px;">
	<span style="font-size:1.4rem;">Montana Cans Flatjet Cap Wide, Red/Black:</span>
</h1>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	<a href="/Black%20Spray%20Paint" rel="">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07FPN6SMV?ref_=ppx_hzsearch_conn_dt_b_fed_asin_title_6&amp;th=1</a>
</p>

<p>
	—————————————
</p>

<p>
	<strong>Brand: Montana Black</strong>
</p>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	<strong>Item</strong> - <u>Paint Color</u>
</p>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	<strong>Armor &amp; Jet Pack</strong> - <a href="https://www.dickblick.com/items/montana-black-spray-paint-storm-400-ml-can/" rel="external nofollow">BLK 6530 / Storm</a>
</p>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	<br /><strong>Shoulders/knees &amp; jet pack thruster trim</strong> - <a href="https://www.dickblick.com/items/montana-black-spray-paint-melon-yellow-400-ml-can/" rel="external nofollow">BLK 1045/Melon</a>
</p>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	<strong>gauntlets &amp; jet pack greebly trim</strong> - <a href="https://www.dickblick.com/items/montana-black-spray-paint-cardinal-400-ml-can/" rel="external nofollow">BLK 3062 Cardinal</a>
</p>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	Thanks to <a data-ipshover="" data-ipshover-target="https://thebhg.net/forum/index.php?/profile/13563-ru4scuba/&amp;do=hovercard&amp;referrer=https%253A%252F%252Fthebhg.net%252Fforum%252Findex.php%253F%252Ftopic%252F6779-wip-another-boba-fresh-build%252F" href="https://thebhg.net/forum/index.php?/profile/13563-ru4scuba/" rel="" style="background-color:transparent;color:inherit;font-size:16px;" title="Go to Ru4scuba's profile">Ru4scuba[BH]</a> for listing the paints needed (click out <a href="https://thebhg.net/forum/index.php?/topic/6779-wip-another-boba-fresh-build/&amp;do=findComment&amp;comment=74980" rel="">their build thread</a>).
