			<p>
	<u>Girth Belt</u>
</p>

<p>
	 
</p>

<p style="color:#bfbfbf;font-size:14px;">
	I ordered rope from <a href="https://www.pethardware.com/en/ropes/rope-black-tan-brown-817/?v=RO12/BTB" rel="external nofollow">Pet Hardware in Croatia</a> - fyi shipping is expensive.  Per CRL Rope diameter will vary depending on body size of the costumer (10 mm – 14 mm).  This is good enough for basic approval.
</p>

<p>
	My wife helped finish modifying the gloves and sewed the girth belt together this weekend!
</p>

<p>
	We followed this video: 
</p>

<div class="ipsEmbeddedVideo">
	<div>
		<iframe allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="113" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/Kv_xp2TZU5M?feature=oembed" title="BOBA FETT'S girth belt .....tutorial" width="200"></iframe>
	</div>
</div>

<p>
	<u>Gloves</u>
</p>

<p>
	The Screen used gloves were actually 2 gloves.  A pair of Stompers Patrol-X 1.0 Chestnut inside of a pair of Black on the outside with fingers cut off.  The 1.0 has depleted from stock, but they were replaced by the <a href="https://stompersgloves.com/patrol-x-glove/" rel="external nofollow">Stompers Patrol-X 2.0 Gloves</a>.  They look the same but with stronger inseam.
</p>

<p>
	<img alt="0nuhZlM.jpeg" class="ipsImage" data-ratio="75.00" height="1200" width="1200" src="https://i.imgur.com/0nuhZlM.jpeg" /></p>

<p>
